Test scenario: Categories

TC_1
Test case: Categories group is on homepage
Test steps:
1. Go to AUT
2. Categories group should be displayed
3. Verify there are 3 categories: Phones, Laptops, Monitors

TC_2
Test case: Phones category
1. Go to AUT
2. Stay on home page
3. filter products by Phones category
4. Verify that only phone products are displayed


TC_3
Test case: Phones category
1. Go to AUT
2. Stay on home page
3. filter products by Laptops category
4. Verify that only laptop products are displayed


TC_4
Test case: Monitors category
1. Go to AUT
2. Stay on home page
3. filter products by Monitors category
4. Verify that only monitors products are displayed